  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00001",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林黛玉上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00002",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "一点秋心，声淅沥，风雨黄昏。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00003",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "半卷香帘半掩门，秋闺怨女试啼痕。娇羞默默凭谁诉，倦意西风夜已昏。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00004",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "奴家、林黛玉。幼失怙恃，工愁多病，寄人篱下，日掩啼痕。这且不在话下。近因秋分之后，旧症复发，比之往年，又觉加重。这几日养病房中，不知谁来与我遣闷。正是：",
      "text_length": 76
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00005",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "家远愁看花姊妹，病多难配药君臣。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00006",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛宝钗上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00007",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "薛宝钗"
      ],
      "text": "一院秋深苔未扫，透帘烹药气先迎。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00008",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛宝钗进门。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00009",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛宝钗"
      ],
      "text": "啊颦妹妹哪里？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00010",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "原来是宝姐姐，请坐！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00011",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛宝钗"
      ],
      "text": "有坐。你这几日病体如何？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00012",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "依然如此，无有起色。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00013",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛宝钗"
      ],
      "text": "据为姐看来，这几位太医虽说高明，但你吃他们的药，总不见效。不如另请高手，与你瞧上一瞧，把病治好，岂不是好？照你这样，一年四季，都病病恹恹，也不是常法呀！",
      "text_length": 76
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00014",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "咳，姐姐呀！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00015",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "自古道生和死其权在天，总使有卢医扁鹊亦枉然。我自知飘零人福薄命短，姑不辞日与这药鼎为缘。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00016",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛宝钗"
      ],
      "text": "你这话可不是这样说法，古人云：食谷者生。你平常饮食太少，我看你那药方上，人参肉桂又太多，都不是养生之道。我给你想一个法子，每日早晨，用银吊子熬点燕窝粥吃，最是滋阴补气。大概你的病就可以好了。",
      "text_length": 95
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00017",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "咳！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00018",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "论知己我与你缘分非浅，吐微衷掬肺腑听我一言。今日参明日术已惹人厌，更何苦求燕窝花样新鲜！",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00019",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "想妹妹我乃无依无靠之人，何苦叫人讨厌于我！",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00020",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛宝钗"
      ],
      "text": "如此说来，你我都是一样。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00021",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀呀，我如何比得姐姐，你有房有地，又有哥哥，又有母亲，住在这里，又不占他们一丝半缕。妹妹我一无所有，一草一木借得仰仗于人，我焉能比得你呀！",
      "text_length": 70
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00022",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛宝钗"
      ],
      "text": "将来也不过多费一份嫁妆罢了，如今也愁不到哪里呀？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00023",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "人家当你知己，与你商量肺腑，你反将人取笑，真乃岂有此理！",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00024",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "薛宝钗"
      ],
      "text": "不必学司马牛顾影自叹，我与你同作客俱是一般。且将息暂分别独居小院，冒斜风带细雨罗袂生寒。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00025",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛宝钗下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00026",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "哎！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00027",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "生平知己有多少？可与人言无二三。闲取诗篇灯下看，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00028",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林黛玉看书。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00029",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "且喜新词写花笺。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00030",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "且住！想诗词乃是心有所感发为文章，奴家何不拟这“春江花月夜”之格，就以“秋创风雨夕”为题！",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00031",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林黛玉写诗词。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00032",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "秋花惨淡秋草黄，耿耿秋灯秋夜长；已觉秋窗秋不尽，哪堪风雨助凄凉！助风秋雨来何速？惊破秋窗秋梦绿；抱得秋情不忍眠，自问秋屏移泪烛。泪烛摇摇爇短檠，牵愁照恨动离情；谁家秋院无风人，何处秋窗无雨声？罗衾不耐秋风力，残漏声催秋雨急；连宵脉脉复飕飕，灯前似伴离人泣。寒烟小院转萧条，疏竹虚窗时滴沥；不知风雨几时休，已教泪洒窗纱湿。",
      "text_length": 160
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00033",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾宝玉上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00034",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "绕回廊穿曲径雨寒风劲，灯如豆人影恍位闻夜吟。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00035",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾宝玉推门。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00036",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "妹妹，你今日病体如何？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00037",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "我道是谁？原来是哪里来的一个渔翁啊！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00038",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林黛玉笑，贾宝玉看。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00039",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "今日气色好了。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00040",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾宝玉脱蓑衣。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00041",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "你头上戴笠，身上披蓑，难道你这双鞋儿，就不怕雨湿了么？",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00042",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "这金藤笠，玉针蓑，还有一双沙棠屐，乃是一袭。是我将它脱在廊下了。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00043",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "原来如此。这蓑笠倒也精巧。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00044",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "此乃北静王所赠。妹妹若是见喜，我便弄一套来送与妹妹。你请看这笠儿，若是冬天遮雪，岂不大妙。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00045",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "我却消受不起，要是戴上这个，不成了画上和戏上扮的渔婆子了么。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00046",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林黛玉羞。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00047",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "呀，这是妹妹新诗，待我看来。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00048",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾宝玉看诗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00049",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "真乃绝妙好词。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00050",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林黛玉夺笺。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00051",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "虽然是烧了，我已将它熟记在心里。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00052",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "我要安歇了。你请回去吧，明日再来。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00053",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，有打扰妹妹你劳神，我要去了。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00054",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "披玉针戴金笠今宵暂别，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00055",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "慢着！你有灯笼无有？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00056",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "外面有一盏羊角灯。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00057",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "羊角灯不亮，把这玻璃灯与你，你自己提着吧。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00058",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "恐怕失脚滑倒将它打破！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00059",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "一个灯笼能值几何？跌了人儿，那就值得多了。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00060",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "原来如此。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00061",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "风飘飘雨潇潇珍重安歇。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00062",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾宝玉下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00063",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "唉！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00064",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "林黛玉"
      ],
      "text": "眼前人都不见芳心无赖，对孤灯听秋雨顾影徘徊。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03057006_e00065",
      "play_id": "03057006",
      "scene_id": "03057006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林黛玉下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}